  %h2 2. Adding Runtime Configuration to a Deployable

  %p
  Open the deployable:
  %ol
    %li
    Click on the 
    %b Administer tab
    &rArr; <b>Content</b>. This displays a list of your catalogues.
    %li
    Choose a catalog with deployables to edit. Click on the Name link.
    %li
